Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBGroup

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBGroup
public class JDBGroup extends Object
The JDBGroup class is used to insert/update and delete records from the SYS_GROUPS table. The table is part of the security / permissions within the application.
